        function Hd = butterworth(order, cutoffFreq1, cutoffFreq2, sampleRate, ~, ~)
            %BUTTERWORTH Returns a discrete-time filter object.

            % MATLAB Code
            % Generated by MATLAB(R) 25.2 and Signal Processing Toolbox 25.2.
